data.description: Speaking of beautiful quiet communities to live in, come see this beautiful spacious newer home located in the sought after community of Vista Reserve in Apopka. This home features 5 bedrooms 3 full bathrooms and a layout that make it a cozy very functional home. An integrated spacious kitchen with beautiful details is a chef oasis for anyone who enjoys cooking. The backyard is an open canvas for you to customize it as  your own outdoor paradise and enjoy the Florida weather all year long. Make your appointment to come see it!
